                        <interp inst="t18411025-2611-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi> of an Assault. Aged 37.—
<rs id="t18411025-2611-punishment-67" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18411025-2611-punishment-67" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
