                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2611-18411025 t18411025-2611-punishment-67"></join>Confined One Month</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Lord Chief Baron Abinger.</hi>
